    <li>The first signs went live on 1 April 2014 at Vauxhall bus station, closely followed by two in Harrow on 2 May and 27 June 2014.  Victoria Coach Station had a sign installed on 14 March 2015.  East Croydon was installed on 27 March 2015; two signs were installed in Walthamstow on 29 April 2015 and both North Greenwich signs were installed on 11 May 2015</li>
